<br>
Not that it really matters…  it just struck me a little sour hearing how entitled you feel about having every pet be better.<br>
<br>
Here’s my personal take on pets… we should get “Bane” pets that can be summoned only in certain zones. In Temple of Veeshan you should get a pet that’s on par with the mobs you find in that zone. It would keep us from slaughtering lesser zones and still give us a viable upgrade in the new worlds. Necromancers should get something similar. (Perhaps an undead or possessed or resurrected version.)<br>
<br>
Might fix a lotta things...<br>
